# World and Book Conventions

## World Index

- `layout: world`
- `world: <slug>` (matches directory)
- `order` for main page listing

## Book Index

- `layout: book`
- `world`, `book: <slug>` (matches directory)
- `order` for world page listing

## Content

- World: intro to the setting, themes, what readers can expect
- Book: blurb, description, tone
